nodes.text: Doshian jellyfish were marine invertebrates native to Trandosha. They were widely considered to be the Trandoshan's favorite food.
Many homesick Trandoshan travelers used to carry around a jellyfish hologram.
Jellyfish holograms are often found on killed Trandoshans on the Avatar Orbital Platform in Rage of the Wookiees, the second expansion of the MMORPG Star Wars Galaxies.
